{"TopicId":170721,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"\u0026quot;Terminate All Debris\u0026quot; Button","CreatedByName":"CosmicCharlie","CreatedById":150762,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-10T03:17:35Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"CosmicCharlie","CreatedById":150762,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-10T03:17:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEOM\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-10T03:23:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEOM?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs far as the request, it would be handy, but there is essentially a way to do it.\u00A0 You can set how many pieces of debris you want the game to keep track of before it starts deleting.\u00A0 I do believe that slider goes down to 0.\u00A0 You can set it to 0, load your save, save it again, then go turn the setting back up, and all the debris should be gone.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBe careful though, remember, it treats anything without a command pod or probe core as debris.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-02-10T03:23:48Z\u0022 title=\u002202/10/2018 03:23  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 10, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Geonovast\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CosmicCharlie","CreatedById":150762,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-10T04:39:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEnd Of Message.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ace in Space","CreatedById":184431,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-10T04:43:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree 100%. Just the other day I was thinking about this as I manually deleted debris.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, or better yet - the ability to select multiple craft (by holding ctrl probably) and then a \u0022delete all selected\u0022 button. This would bypass the issue Geonovast pointed out where the game treats things that are potentially not really debris as debris. Just click down the list and hit the delete button once.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-10T16:57:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExist On Mods\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-11T21:39:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223291352\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022170721\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221518281822\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022166502\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spricigo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/02/2018 at 4:57 PM, Spricigo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExist On Mods\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut that doesn\u0027t mean it\u0027s not a good idea for stock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MiffedStarfish","CreatedById":175356,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-11T21:46:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExcellent idea, sounds very handy for space battle cleanup.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-11T22:15:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake a MUUUUUD!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Mod)\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-12T01:50:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223292449\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022170721\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221518385140\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022130621\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022pandaman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, pandaman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut that doesn\u0027t mean it\u0027s not a good idea for stock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nActually the statment carry no significance about the idea being good or bad, for stock or for mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-12T06:14:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223292632\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022170721\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221518400207\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022166502\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spricigo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Spricigo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nActually the statment carry no significance about the idea being good or bad, for stock or for mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTrue. You\u00A0made no indication of your thoughts on that, and nor did i for that matter.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor me it\u0027s one of those things that if it\u0027s there then fine, but i never felt the need for it personally.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo offence intended.\u00A0 My response was simply to express my opinion that just because a feature exists in a mod it does not mean there is not an argument for it to be included in stock.\u00A0 Not every play wants to use mods and not every player (consoles in particular) has tbe option to.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MinimalMinmus","CreatedById":172387,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-12T22:58:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould definitely save a few clicks, especially after high \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EdV\u003C/abbr\u003E low tech missions, that tend to leave debris everywhere.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}